snippet.title: "That's Enough!" Judge Loses It After Amber Heard Asks For Case Dismissal!
snippet.description:
The Judge Loses His Temper Silencing Amber Heard After She Asks For A Case Dismissal For The Third Time!

✅ Subscribe & HIT that notification bell for more Celebrity Content!

"“Amber is not a product of domestic maltreatment, she is a perpetrator”, says the suit that her ex-husband Johny Depp filed against her.

Although fans believed they had seen everything after such a turbulent situation between Amber Heard and the legendary star Johnny Depp, recently the movie star Amber Heard continues giving what to talk about by trying again to get the court to dismiss the case between her and Johnny, this time for the third time.
But will it work for her? Will the judges really consider this move and let Amber and her Legal team get away with it?"

#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp
